des: This Channel focuses on Real Estate education for the regular Joe. Content covers the journey of real estate and addresses things you need. From fixing your credit to knowing that escrow may not go smoothly, but that is the norm! Let us help you understand what you need to expect and do, to help make your life easier knowing that you are not alone.
